dct_description_sm: This collection of flat maps, prepared from November of 2018 through January of 2020 by Data You Can Use, present a variety of neighborhood indicators for the City of Milwaukee. All maps utilize 2010 Census tracts. For more information, please visit Data  You Can Use.
